    "/plan \"the apps/plugin listing scraping for the home-search-ca is not reading the class from the span element containing the price. The class indicates the scale of the price <span class=\"k\"> indicates that the price in thousands. here is an example : <div data-v-25fad36a=\"\" class=\"item price Sale\"><span data-v-36de0806=\"\" data-v-25fad36a=\"\" class=\"k\">680</span></div>\"",
