    "uh oh! Now are enrichment script is throwing errors we can't see as it doesn't reuse the existing tab but is forcing to use a new tab.",
    "update the output data object. swap 'hscBrokerInfo' for 'brokerInfo', 'hscPropertyDetails' for 'propertyDetails', 'hscRooms' for 'rooms'. Also replace the data.description with the tokenizedDescription.aboutProperty value. Additionally, the mlsNumber for a 'home-search-ca' enrichement is 9 characters and starts with the letter 'X'. If the propertyDetails.status is 'for Sale' then the listingType is 'for-sale'. The propertyDetails keys should be in camelcase. propertyDetails.basement is an array of comma separated strings that need to be deduplicated, the same goes for the propertyDetails.exterior.",
